<L>Of all the worthies &s;ince recorded time,</L>
<L N="155">A&s;cend the lucid hall. Again &s;he &s;ounds</L>
<L>A mea&s;ure &s;weeter than the Dorian flute</L>
<L>Of Pan, or lyre of Phoebus; each a&s;&s;umes</L>
