<LG>
<L>The &s;wift forerunners of th' imperial camp</L>
<L>Ere long Mardonius joins, where Athens-lifts</L>
<L><PB N="95" REF="104">
Her tow'rs in pro&s;pect. Unexpected &s;een,</L>
<L N="179">Their mighty chief with gen'ral, cordial &s;houts</L>
<L>They greet; their multitude, their tran&s;port, clear</L>
<L>His heart from trouble. Soon Barbarian throngs</L>
<L>With &s;hading &s;tandards through Cephi&s;&s;us wade,</L>
