<LG>
<PB N="96" REF="105">
<L>Is this the city who&s;e pre&s;umption dar'd</L>
<L>Invade the lord of A&s;ia? &s;ternly &s;aid</L>
<L>Mardonius ent'ring; whither now are fled</L>
<L>Th' audacious train, who&s;e firebrands Sardis felt?</L>
<L N="200">Where'er you lurk, Athenians, if in &s;ight,</L>
