<LG>
<L N="255">Approving, Leontiades, thy words</L>
<L>I hear; Ma&s;i&s;tius, thee my &s;ervant loves,</L>
<L>Mardonius, always victor in my name;</L>
<L>Yet learn at la&s;t, O &s;atrap! who do&s;t wear</L>
<L>The fulle&s;t honours, to partake with me,</L>
