<L><PB N="102" REF="113">
Gho&s;t of my father! lift thy awful brow;</L>
<L>Rememb'ring now th' Athenians, &s;ee thy &s;on</L>
<L N="305">On their pre&s;umptuous heads retaliate flames:</L>
<L>Depriv'd of burial, &s;hall their bodies leave</L>
<L>Pale &s;pectres here to wail their city fall'n,</L>
