<LG>
<L N="330">Before the Prytanaeum &s;tops the car.</L>
<L>Now &s;avage bands inclo&s;e that rev'rend &s;eat</L>
<L>Of judgment; there Mardonius waits. The king,</L>
<L>Pleas'd with his care, &s;alutes him: Thou ha&s;t long</L>
<L>Sweat under harne&s;s in th' eternal &s;nows</L>
<L N="335">Of Macedon and Thracia, ha&s;t my name</L>
<L>There dre&s;s'd in ample trophies; but thy &s;peed,</L>
<L>Preventing my arrival, is unknown</L>
